        <Parent_String>tabernacles (liturgical containers) [300207778], liturgical containers [300194500], ceremonial containers [300197576], containers by function or context [300197200], containers (receptacles) [300197197], Containers (hierarchy name) [300045611], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
